# CayleyPy Pancake Research

- Use `CayleyPy_Pancake/` only for pancake-specific work and for extracting reusable engineering patterns.
- Keep local docs, code, experiments, and conclusions inside the project.
- Do not treat this project as the universal execution layer for all competitions.
- If a new competition needs active work, prefer a dedicated isolated subproject.
